Actress Heather Locklear arrested for driving under the influence of drugs
Actress Heather Locklear, favorite Amanda from the Melrose Place series, was arrested this weekend in Santa Barbara, California for driving under the influence of drugs.
A witness saw her perform unusual maneuvers as she tried to leave a parking lot in Montecito, a California road patrol spokesman told People magazine.
